<td colspan=2 bgcolor=beige style="border-top:1px solid black;"><strong>Vocabulary</strong>
<br>bilik = room<br>
air (it was formerly spelt ayer) = water<br>
bilik air = washroom<br>
kasut = shoes<br>
pejabat pos = post office<br>
kunci = key
</tr>
